'''Bill Gates''' ([[1955-ngièn]] 10-ngie̍t 28-ngit －）, he yit-miàng [[Mî-koet]] [[khî-ngia̍p-kâ]], [[ngiôn-thí kûng-tshàng-sṳ̂]], [[tshṳ̀-san-kâ]] yî-khi̍p [[Mì-ngiôn Kûng-sṳ̂]] ke Túng-sṳ-tshòng. Tsó-ngièn kì lâu Paul Allen yit-hí tshóng-li̍p Mì-ngiôn Kûng-sṳ̂, tsên-ngim Mì-ngiôn CEO lâu sú-sit [[ngiôn-thí sat-kie-sṳ̂]], pin tshṳ̀-yû kûng-sṳ̂ tshêu-ko 8% ke [[phû-thûng kú]], ya-he kûng-sṳ̂ chui-thai ke ke-ngìn [[kú-tûng]]. [[1995-ngièn]] to [[2007-ngièn]] ke Forbes tshiòn-khiù yi-van fu-vung phài-hòng póng-chûng, Bill Gates
lièn-siu̍k sṳ̍p-sâm ngièn he sṳ-kie sú-fu, kì yúng-yû ńg-pak pat-sṳ̍p yi [[Mî-kîm]] ke-ngìn tshòi-sán. [[2008-ngièn]] liuk-ngie̍t ngi-sṳ̍p-tshit ngit tsṳn-sṳt thui-tshut Mì-ngiôn Kûng-sṳ̂.

